<topic id="xslt-outline">
  <title>XSLT Outline View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>XSLT<indexterm>Outline view</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_v51_cgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view for XSLT stylesheets displays the list of all the
      components (templates, attribute-sets, character-maps, variables, functions, keys, outputs)
      from both the edited stylesheet and its imports or includes. For XSL and XSD resources, the
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view collects its components starting from the <xref
        keyref="glossentry_main-file"><term>main files</term></xref>. The main files can be
      defined in the project or in the associated validation scenario. For further details about the
        <term>Main Files</term> support go to <xref
        href="defining_main_files.dita#defining_main_files">Defining Main Files at Project
        Level</xref>.</p>
    <p id="p_w51_cgk_54b">By default, it is displayed on the left side of the editor. <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"/></p>
    <p id="p_x51_cgk_54b">
      <fig product="editor developer" id="fig_y51_cgk_54b">
        <title>XSLT Outline View</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_xslt_outliner.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_z51_cgk_54b">
      <fig product="editorEclipse developerEclipse" id="fig_av1_cgk_54b">
        <title>XSLT Outline View</title>
        <image href="../img/ec_xslt_outliner.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_bv1_cgk_54b">The following actions are available in the <ph product="editor developer"><uicontrol><image
            href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_bvj_ngd_cs"/>Settings</uicontrol> menu on the
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view toolbar</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse developerEclipse"><uicontrol>View Menu</uicontrol> on the
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view action bar</ph>:<dl id="dl_cv1_cgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_dv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Filter returns exact matches</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The text filter of the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view returns only exact
            matches;</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_ev1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CaretUpdateOff16.png" id="image_km1_vft_tr"/>Selection
              update on cursor move</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Controls the synchronization between <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view and source
            document. The selection in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view can be synchronized
            with the cursor moves or the changes in the XSLT editor. Selecting one of the components
            from the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view also selects the corresponding item in the
            source document.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
    <p id="p_fv1_cgk_54b">When the <uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_vlg_kfg_ks"/>Show
        components</uicontrol> option is selected, the following actions are available:</p>
    <p id="p_gv1_cgk_54b">
      <dl id="dl_hv1_cgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_iv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" placement="inline"
                id="image_pcy_4hg_ks"/>Show XML structure</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays the XML document structure in a tree-like structure.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_jv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Show all components</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays all components that were collected starting from the <xref
              keyref="glossentry_main-file"><term>main file</term></xref>. This option is set by
            default.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline_schema_outline_view" id="dlentry_kv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_lv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Group by location/type</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The stylesheet components can be grouped by location and type.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
    <p id="p_mv1_cgk_54b">When the <uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_v2n_gfg_ks"/>Show XML
        structure</uicontrol> option is selected, the following actions are available:</p>
    <p id="p_nv1_cgk_54b">
      <dl id="dl_ov1_cgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_pv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_xky_jht_tr"/>Show
              components</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Switches the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view to the components display mode.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline-flat-presentation-mode" id="dlentry_qv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline_show_comments" id="dlentry_rv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/show_element_name" id="dlentry_sv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/comments_sjow_text" id="dlentry_tv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline_show_attributes" id="dlentry_uv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline-configure-displayed-attrs" id="dlentry_vv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
    <p id="p_wv1_cgk_54b">The following contextual menu actions are also available when the <uicontrol><image
          href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_cpg_z3g_ks"/>Show components</uicontrol>
      option is selected in the <ph product="editor developer"><uicontrol><image
            href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_ulj_1jg_ks"/>Settings</uicontrol> menu</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse developerEclipse"><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol></ph>: </p>
    <p id="p_xv1_cgk_54b">
      <dl id="dl_yv1_cgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_zv1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Attribute16.gif"/>Edit Attributes</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens a small in-place editor that allows you to edit the attributes of the selected
            node.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_aw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Cut16.png" id="image_ukv_gz1_5r"/>Cut</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Cuts the currently selected node.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_bw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_a1v_mst_tr"
            />Copy</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Copies the currently selected node.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_cw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" placement="inline"
                id="image_s2y_phd_cs"/>Delete</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Deletes the currently selected node.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_dw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/SearchReferences16.png" placement="inline"/>Search
              References</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_shift_r"/></dt>
          <dd>Searches all references of the item found at current cursor position in the defined
            scope, if any. See <xref
              href="find-xslt-references-and-declarations.dita#find-xslt-references-and-declarations"
              format="dita">Finding XSLT References and Declarations</xref> for more details.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_ew1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Search References in</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Searches all references of the item found at current cursor position in the specified
            scope. See <xref
              href="find-xslt-references-and-declarations.dita#find-xslt-references-and-declarations"
              format="dita">Finding XSLT References and Declarations</xref> for more details.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_fw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Component Dependencies</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="xslt-component-dependencies.dita#xslt-component-dependencies"
                ><uicontrol>Component Dependencies</uicontrol> view</xref> that allows you to see
            the dependencies for the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_gw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt>Show referenced resources</dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="xslt-hierarchy-view.dita#xslt-hierarchy-view"
                ><uicontrol>Referenced/Dependent Resources</uicontrol> view</xref> that displays the
            references for the currently selected resource.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_hw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt>Show dependent resources</dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="xslt-hierarchy-view.dita#xslt-hierarchy-view"
                ><uicontrol>Referenced/Dependent Resources</uicontrol> view</xref> that displays the
            dependencies of the currently selected resource.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_iw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RenameXSLResource16.png" id="image_u5q_rv1_5r"/>Rename
              Component in</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Renames the selected component. See <xref
              href="xslt-refactoring-actions.dita#xslt-refactoring-actions" format="dita">XSLT
              Refactoring Actions</xref> for more details.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
    <p id="p_jw1_cgk_54b">The following contextual menu actions are available in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol>
      view when the <uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_dvn_cjg_ks"/>Show
        XML structure</uicontrol> option is selected in the <ph product="editor developer"
            ><uicontrol><image href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_evn_cjg_ks"
          />Settings</uicontrol> menu</ph><ph product="editorEclipse developerEclipse"
          ><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol></ph>:</p>
    <p id="p_kw1_cgk_54b">
      <dl id="dl_lw1_cgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_mw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Append Child</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays a list of elements that you can insert as children of the current
            element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_nw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Insert Before</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays a list of elements that you can insert as siblings of the current element,
            before the current element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_ow1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Insert After</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays a list of elements that you can insert as siblings of the current element,
            after the current element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_pw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Attribute16.gif"/>Edit Attributes</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens a small in-place editor that allows you to edit the attributes of the selected
            node.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_qw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/ToggleComment16.png" id="image_bsr_brd_cs"/>Toggle
              Comment</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Comments/uncomments the currently selected element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_rw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/SearchReferences16.png" placement="inline"
                id="image_tzy_njg_ks"/>Search references</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Searches for the references of the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_sw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Search references in</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Searches for the references of the currently selected component in the context of a
            scope that you define.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_tw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/ComponentDependencies16.png" id="image_q2l_j3t_tr"
              />Component dependencies</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="xslt-component-dependencies.dita#xslt-component-dependencies"
                ><uicontrol>Component Dependencies</uicontrol> view</xref> that displays the
            dependencies of the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_uw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RenameXSLResource16.png" id="image_rpj_mv1_5r"/>Rename
              Component in</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Renames the currently selected component in the context of a scope that you
            define.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_vw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Cut16.png" id="image_u1f_hz1_5r"/>Cut</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Cuts the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_ww1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_x2z_mst_tr"
            />Copy</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Copies the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_xw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" placement="inline"
                id="image_uzy_njg_ks"/>Delete</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Deletes the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_yw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol product="developer editor"><image href="../img/ExpandAll16.png"
                placement="inline" id="image_lny_prd_cs"/>Expand More</uicontrol><uicontrol
              product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><image href="../img/ExpandAll16.png"
                placement="inline" id="image_ywc_f1j_cs"/>Expand All</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Expands the structure of a component in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_zw1_cgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CollapseAll16.png" id="image_yl1_r3t_tr"/>Collapse
              All</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Collapses the structure of all the component in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol>
            view.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
    <p id="p_ax1_cgk_54b">The stylesheet components information is presented on two columns: the first column presents
      the <xmlatt>name</xmlatt> and <xmlatt>match</xmlatt> attributes, the second column the
        <xmlatt>mode</xmlatt> attribute. If you know the component name, match or mode, you can
      search it in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view by typing one of these pieces of
      information in the filter text field from the top of the view or directly on the tree
      structure. When you type de component name, match or mode in the text field, you can switch to
      the tree structure using:</p>
    <ul id="ul_bx1_cgk_54b">
      <li id="li_cx1_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Keyboard arrow keys</li>
      <li id="li_dx1_cgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol><shortcut>Enter</shortcut></uicontrol> key</li>
      <li id="li_ex1_cgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol><shortcut>Tab</shortcut></uicontrol> key</li>
      <li id="li_fx1_cgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol><shortcut>Shift-Tab</shortcut></uicontrol> key combination</li>
    </ul>
    <p id="p_gx1_cgk_54b">To switch from tree structure to the filter text field, you can use
          <uicontrol><shortcut>Tab</shortcut></uicontrol> and
          <uicontrol><shortcut>Shift-Tab</shortcut></uicontrol>.</p>
    <note type="tip" id="note_hx1_cgk_54b">The search filter is case insensitive. The following wildcards are accepted:<ul id="ul_ix1_cgk_54b">
        <li id="li_jx1_cgk_54b" irina="irina"><b>*</b> - any string</li>
        <li id="li_kx1_cgk_54b" irina="irina"><b>?</b> - any character</li>
        <li id="li_lx1_cgk_54b" irina="irina"><b>,</b> - patterns separator</li>
      </ul>If no wildcards are specified, the string to search is used as a partial match.</note>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/synchronized_views" id="p_mx1_cgk_54b"/>
    <p id="p_nx1_cgk_54b"><ph keyref="product"/> allows you to sort the components of the tree in the
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view.<note id="note_ox1_cgk_54b">Sorting groups in the
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view is not supported. </note>
      <ph keyref="product"/> has a predefined order of the groups in the
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view:<ul id="ul_tg4_3fm_2g">
        <li id="li_px1_cgk_54b" irina="irina">For location, the names of the files are sorted alphabetically. The file you are editing
          is located at the top of the list.</li>
        <li id="li_qx1_cgk_54b" irina="irina">For type, the order is: parameters, variables, templates, functions, set attributes,
            character-map.<note id="note_rx1_cgk_54b">When no grouping is available and the table is not sorted, <ph
              keyref="product"/> sorts the components depending on their order in the document. <ph
              keyref="product"/> also takes into account the name of the file that the components
            are part of. </note></li>
      </ul></p>
